p: Similarly, at NS1 residue 264 (polyprotein residue1058), there is a change from Val to Met in Thailand 2006 and Cambodia 2010, and Met is present as consensus in samples from pre-epidemic and epidemic cases, whereas the Malaysia strain has Val ( S2 Table). However, Val is still present as a variant in samples prior to and during the epidemic. Val is detected at 4.2% in Illumina data from French Polynesia stock virus (Bioproject PRJNA316976) and maintained during passage in two macaques at 4.2 and 9.9%.
